. They hunt in pairs and will sometimes join small feeding flocks. The red-faced woodland warbler is not considered threatened by human activities. It has a small worldwide range but is relatively common where it occurs. It is classified as least concern by the IUCN. References", "shortSummary": "The red-faced woodland warbler (Phylloscopus laetus) is a species of leaf warbler in the family Phylloscopidae. It forms a superspecies wit…", "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9f/Redfacedwoodwarbler.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-phylloscopus", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-phylloscopus-laetus", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-phylloscopus", "species": "taxonomy-species-phylloscopus-laetus"}, "expandable": true, "x": -73.59, "y": -451.22, "z": -433.78}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-phylloscopus", "name": "Phylloscopus", "latinName": "Phylloscopus", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Phylloscopus（Phylloscopus）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联80种鸟类，如Western Bonelli's warbler、Eastern Bonelli's warbler、橙斑翅柳莺等80种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 80, "x": -485.52, "y": -456.13, "z": 92.65}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-phylloscopus-laetus", "name": "Red-faced woodland warbler", "latinName": "Phylloscopus laetus", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Red-faced woodland warbler（Phylloscopus laetus）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Red-faced woodland warbler。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": -73.59, "y": -451.22, "z": -428.79}], "links": [{"key": "bird-red-faced-woodland-warbler-0fe1b090__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-phylloscopus-laetus", "source": "bird-red-faced-woodland-warbler-0fe1b090", "target": "taxonomy-species-phylloscopus-laetus", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属